{"tid":1906250,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「讀書須父幹」有幾多真係靠自己讀到大學神科畢業？（2）","createTime":"2020-03-01T20:09:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T00:25:37.000Z","uid":68944,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ec3e60725f184f220ec4c06a532d2271a99503e2","tid":1906250,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"144277bbbe87e3877ccb3ee46fae7b16732e001a","tid":1906250,"uid":181819,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T20:17:16.000Z","msg":"咁多嗲做乜<br />\n成班怨天尤人窮撚好似港女咁要人氹<br />\n係呀認命啦 個個讀得成書做專業人士邊個做D萬零蚊既工呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />認清自己位置早日接受現實啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9bdabcc84c334c64f128549d86026ad11c70249","tid":1906250,"uid":255802,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T21:10:29.000Z","msg":"諗起之前係國際law firm到做<br />\nTrainee要做1年多啲 <br />\n大概幾個人跟1個partner級嘅學野 <br />\n完左留得低就50k up + admission <br />\n<br />\n咁我就發現黎interview trainee嘅<br />\n屋企地址都係九龍港島私樓<br />\n再望下個大學都係Cambridge Oxford Yale<br />\n成功in到嘅有少部份人原來本身識啲大粒野<br />\n<br />\n原來真係有啲人一出世就係唔同啲<br />\n無論係機遇定實力 有時真係命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df6589f1d901e97570fab402820c1736239bf6d1","tid":1906250,"uid":104149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T21:17:06.000Z","msg":"咁sad既 <br />\n認清自己咩位置係咪代表一世都要企係同一個位"},{"pid":"2a948fcd61d1887cdad6a0b7ae931653acdce9e6","tid":1906250,"uid":323922,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T23:29:06.000Z","msg":"窮撚居屋，父母中小學畢業，外國長春藤大學博士畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0f4f2136bd93983dda83140be2bfd6fb6e12a9","tid":1906250,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9bdabcc84c334c64f128549d86026ad11c70249","tid":1906250,"uid":255802,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T21:10:29.000Z","msg":"諗起之前係國際law firm到做<br />\nTrainee要做1年多啲 <br />\n大概幾個人跟1個partner級嘅學野 <br />\n完左留得低就50k up + admission <br />\n<br />\n咁我就發現黎interview trainee嘅<br />\n屋企地址都係九龍港島私樓<br />\n再望下個大學都係Cambridge Oxford Yale<br />\n成功in到嘅有少部份人原來本身識啲大粒野<br />\n<br />\n原來真係有啲人一出世就係唔同啲<br />\n無論係機遇定實力 有時真係命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T23:48:50.000Z","msg":"再補充下 <br />\n雖然屋企背景好大程度影響到你<br />\n但你自己努力真係可以改變好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係個law firm到有個律師對比其他人屋企背景唔係有錢 因為多數後生嘅律師佢地係中學大學都係外國讀 <br />\n( 例如Harrow -&gt;Oxford)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁佢屋企人只係公務員 但佢好比心機讀書 最後入HKU  <br />\n30歲已月入60k up<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40775f949338f086b2a1fffb0985d3c55ce97de2","tid":1906250,"uid":125976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T00:19:51.000Z","msg":"雞腸嚟講出生最大影響，窮撚雞腸好難追<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n理工科就應該窮富差唔多，但如果有相關學術背景家底加持當然好啲<br />\n<br />\n最大影響其實唔係入大學與否，係二世祖嗰份自信你窮撚一世都學唔到，𠵱樣就係有資源同冇資源嘅分別<br />\n<br />\n命（家境、出生地、性別 etc.）就改唔到，唯有捉運（天時、地利）爬上去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c51957784e5e1a768815c12930e83580f79e1f","tid":1906250,"uid":221192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1d0f4f2136bd93983dda83140be2bfd6fb6e12a9","tid":1906250,"uid":255802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9bdabcc84c334c64f128549d86026ad11c70249","tid":1906250,"uid":255802,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T21:10:29.000Z","msg":"諗起之前係國際law firm到做<br />\nTrainee要做1年多啲 <br />\n大概幾個人跟1個partner級嘅學野 <br />\n完左留得低就50k up + admission <br />\n<br />\n咁我就發現黎interview trainee嘅<br />\n屋企地址都係九龍港島私樓<br />\n再望下個大學都係